Class MiniConstraintPanel

java.lang.Object

      java.awt.Container

All Implemented Interfaces:
SchemaTerms, IXEditorPanel, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class MiniConstraintPanel
extends AbstractEditorPanel
implements SchemaTerms

A simple panel with a label (title), a component, and optional buttons. The given label will be at the top, the given component at the left and buttons with given labels on the right. Adds the given listener to the buttons and the list.
